channel.title: Cabac - back to life
channel.description: The Cameroonian Brotherhood Association of Chicago, was founded in 1997 in Chicago. In an act of consciousness of many plagues endured in Africa and a firm resolution not to stand by and do nothing. CABAC was incorporated in the State of Illinois in 2002 and granted the 501 c3 tax status in 2006

item.title: Welcome to Cabac!
item.description:
This Blog is your one stop for all the information related to Cabac meetings and locations as well as driving information and if we are kind enough post meeting pictures.

Check out the Previous website for more info on how painfull this migration process will be.
